trans-unit.source: Provides a component editor for <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpotCollection"></xref> objects in an <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap"></xref> or a similar control.
trans-unit.target: Innehåller en komponent redigerare för <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpotCollection"> </xref> objekt i en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap"> </xref> eller en liknande kontroll.

trans-unit.source: The HotSpotCollectionEditor class provides a user interface for editing the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot> elements of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpotCollection> object that is embedded in an <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap> or a similar control.
trans-unit.target: Klassen HotSpotCollectionEditor ger ett användargränssnitt för att redigera den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot>element i den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpotCollection>objekt som är inbäddad i ett <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap>eller en liknande kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpotCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot>

trans-unit.source: The HotSpotCollectionEditor is invoked by selecting the ellipsis button (**…**) on the **HotSpots** property in the visual designer's **Properties** grid.
trans-unit.target: HotSpotCollectionEditor anropas genom att välja knappen med tre punkter (**... **) på den **Surfpunkter** egenskap i den visuella designern **egenskaper** rutnätet.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.HotSpotCollectionEditor.CanSelectMultipleInstances%2A> method always returns `false` to indicate that only one object can be selected at a time in the editor.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.HotSpotCollectionEditor.CanSelectMultipleInstances%2A>metoden returnerar alltid `false` som anger att endast ett objekt kan väljas i taget i redigeraren.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.HotSpotCollectionEditor.CanSelectMultipleInstances%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.HotSpotCollectionEditor.CreateNewItemTypes%2A> method returns an array of types that the editor can create.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.HotSpotCollectionEditor.CreateNewItemTypes%2A>metoden returnerar en matris av typer som kan skapa redigeraren.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.HotSpotCollectionEditor.CreateNewItemTypes%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.HotSpotCollectionEditor.HelpTopic%2A> property returns the name of the Help topic that the editor displays.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.HotSpotCollectionEditor.HelpTopic%2A>egenskapen returnerar namnet på det hjälpavsnitt som visas i redigeraren.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.HotSpotCollectionEditor.HelpTopic%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.HotSpotCollectionEditor"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.HotSpotCollectionEditor"> </xref> klass.

trans-unit.source: The .NET Framework internally constructs a new instance of the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.HotSpotCollectionEditor> class when you select the ellipsis button (**…**) on the **HotSpots** property in the visual designer's **Properties** grid, when designing an <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap> control or other control that encapsulates a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpotCollection> object.
trans-unit.target: .NET Framework internt skapar en ny instans av klassen <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.HotSpotCollectionEditor>när du väljer på ellipsknappen (**... **) på den **Surfpunkter** egenskap i den visuella designern **egenskaper** rutnätet när du skapar en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap>kontrollen eller andra som kapslar in en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpotCollection>objektet.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpotCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.HotSpotCollectionEditor>

trans-unit.source: The type of the collection to edit.
trans-unit.target: Typ av samlingen för att redigera.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value indicating whether multiple <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot"></xref> collection elements can be selected at one time.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar ett värde som anger om flera <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot"> </xref> samlingselement kan väljas i taget.

trans-unit.source: The CanSelectMultipleInstances method always returns `false`; thus, only one <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot> object can be selected at a time in the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.HotSpotCollectionEditor> object.
trans-unit.target: Metoden CanSelectMultipleInstances returnerar alltid `false`; därför bara en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot>objekt kan väljas i taget i den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.HotSpotCollectionEditor>objekt.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.HotSpotCollectionEditor> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot>

trans-unit.source: Gets the multiple data types that the collection editor can create.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar flera datatyper som kan skapa Mängdredigeraren.

trans-unit.source: The types that the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.HotSpotCollectionEditor> object can create are <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CircleHotSpot>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RectangleHotSpot>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.PolygonHotSpot>, and others that can be derived from the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot> class.
trans-unit.target: Typerna som den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.HotSpotCollectionEditor>objekt kan skapa är <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CircleHotSpot>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RectangleHotSpot>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.PolygonHotSpot>, och andra som kan vara härledd från <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot>klass</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.PolygonHotSpot> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RectangleHotSpot> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CircleHotSpot> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.HotSpotCollectionEditor>

trans-unit.source: A type array of the data types the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.HotSpotCollectionEditor"></xref> can create.
trans-unit.target: En typmatris av datatyper i <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.HotSpotCollectionEditor"> </xref> kan skapa.

trans-unit.source: Gets the Help topic to display for the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.HotSpotCollectionEditor"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar hjälpavsnitt som visas för den <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.HotSpotCollectionEditor"> </xref> objekt.

trans-unit.source: The HelpTopic property gets the name of the Help topic to display when the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.HotSpotCollectionEditor> dialog box **Help** button is clicked or when the **F1** key is pressed.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen HelpTopic hämtar namnet på hjälpavsnitt för att visa när den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.HotSpotCollectionEditor>dialogrutan **hjälp** klickar eller när den **F1** tangenten trycks.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.HotSpotCollectionEditor>

trans-unit.source: A string that specifies the Help topic to display.
trans-unit.target: En sträng som anger hjälpavsnittet ska visas.
